
HC06         Arduino (USB to TTL *)
3.3V(12)     3.3V
Gnd(13)      Gnd
Rx(2)        0->RX   USE 1k-2k voltage splitter for 5V->3.3V shifting
Tx(1)        1<-TX

connect arduino RESET to GND

*) do not comm with atmega328 (arduino) but USB serial converter atmega?u?
   THE OPPOSITE OF SITUATION WITH MultiWii FC and Nano!!


Arduino IDE serial monitor

No line ending, 9600 baud

AT[ENTER]
OK
AT+VERSION[ENTER]
OKlinvorV1.8
AT+BAUD8[ENTER]
OK115200
(change serial monitor to 115200 baud)
AT[ENTER]
OK

