HC06         MultiWii FC (Arduino Nano)
3.3V(12)     3.3V
Gnd(13)      Gnd
Rx(2)        TX1   USE 1k-2k voltage splitter for 5V->3.3V shifting
Tx(1)        RX0


Connect 5V supply e.g. via USB to PC (but DO NOT CONNECT via Software - no comm allowed!)

Open Bluetooth on Android and connect to HC06

Open EZ-GUI on Android select Bluetooth and HC06 then connect.
